    summary: '西班牙国王腓力二世派遣庞大的"无敌舰队"入侵英格兰，被英国海军和风暴击败，标志着西班牙海上霸权的衰落和英国的海上崛起。',
    summaryEn: 'King Philip II of Spain sent his "Invincible Armada" to invade England, only to be defeated by the English navy and storms, marking the decline of Spanish naval hegemony and the rise of English sea power.',
    description: '1588年夏，西班牙国王腓力二世派遣由约130艘战舰、8000名水手和18000名士兵组成的庞大"无敌舰队"入侵英格兰，旨在推翻伊丽莎白一世，恢复天主教在英格兰的统治。英军由霍华德勋爵和德雷克指挥，以更小更敏捷的舰船和远程火炮在朴茨茅斯和加莱海域持续骚扰西班牙舰队。关键时刻，英国人放出8艘火攻船冲入西班牙舰队的锚地，引发混乱。随后在格拉沃利讷海战中，西班牙舰队遭受重创。幸存舰队被迫绕行苏格兰和爱尔兰北部返回，途中遭遇猛烈风暴损失惨重，最终仅约半数船只返回西班牙。此役标志着西班牙欧洲霸权的终结和英国作为一个世界级海上强国的崛起。',
    descriptionEn: 'In the summer of 1588, King Philip II of Spain dispatched his "Invincible Armada" of about 130 ships, 8,000 sailors, and 18,000 soldiers to invade England, aiming to overthrow Elizabeth I and restore Catholicism. The English fleet under Lord Howard and Sir Francis Drake, using smaller, more agile ships with long-range guns, harassed the Spanish in the Channel and off Calais. At a critical moment, the English sent eight fireships into the Spanish anchorage, causing chaos. At the subsequent Battle of Gravelines, the Armada suffered severe damage. The surviving fleet was forced to return home by sailing north around Scotland and Ireland, where violent storms destroyed many more ships. Only about half of the Armada returned to Spain. The defeat marked the end of Spanish European hegemony and the emergence of England as a world naval power.',
